### FIND OUT WHETHER A STUDENT IS PASS OR FAIL , IF IT REQUIRES TOTAL 40% AND AT LEAST 33% , IN EACH SUBJECT TO PASS . ASSUME 3 SUBJECTS AND TAKE MARKS AS AN INPUT FROM THE USER .

# Take marks for 3 subjects
sub1 = float(input("Enter marks of Subject 1: "))
sub2 = float(input("Enter marks of Subject 2: "))
sub3 = float(input("Enter marks of Subject 3: "))

# Assume each subject is out of 100
total = sub1 + sub2 + sub3
percentage = total / 3

# Check pass conditions
if percentage >= 40 and sub1 >= 33 and sub2 >= 33 and sub3 >= 33:
    print("✅ Student is PASS")
else:
    print("❌ Student is FAIL")
